items.name: 侠女/Chinese swordswoman /国风 LORA
items.description:
桃李春风一杯酒,江湖夜雨十年灯。

———— 宋·黄庭坚

大家好，我是chosen鲷，这次带来的是侠女Lora模型。

本次lora其实是我训练国风模型时的一个副产品，因为训练集里面有很多女侠的图片，所以很适合去出侠客风格的图片，同时脸的风格很有中国古典的美感，同时又有点niji的画风，横版竖版均可，分辨率512*768/512*768。关键词Chinese style，记得高清重绘，重绘方式建议ESRGAN_4X，重绘幅度0.5

建议使用我的chosen mix模型,跟其他的大模型相性也还不错，都可以尝试一下，vae搭配蜡笔pastel即可。例图是能够读取tag的，大家可以尝试一下。

感谢大家的下载使用，如果喜欢的话欢迎关注我，我的bilibili pixiv ID均为chosen鲷，欢迎大家关注我的频道https://space.bilibili.com/3867754?spm_id_from=333.1007.0.0，https://www.pixiv.net/users/40911695 谢谢。

Hi, I'm chosen 鲷, and this time I'm here with the Chivalrous Lora model.

This lora is actually a by-product of my training of the Chinese style model, because there are many pictures of women in the training set, so it is very suitable to produce chivalry-style pictures. At the same time, the style of the face is very beautiful in classical China, and at the same time, it is somewhat niji's painting style, both horizontal and vertical versions can be used, with a resolution of 512*768/512*768. Key words: Chinese style, remember HD redrawing, redrawing method is suggested ESRGAN_4X, redrawing range 0.5

It is recommended to use my chosen mix model, which has good compatibility with other large models. You can try all of them, vae with pastel. Example diagram is able to read tag, you can try it.

Thank you for downloading and using, please follow me if you like, my bilibili pixiv ID is chosen Snapper, Welcome to focus on my channel, https://space.bilibili.com/3867754?spm_id_from=333.1007.0.0, https://www.pixiv.net/users/40911695, thank you.

こんにちは、chosen鯛です。今回は任俠女Loraモデルをお持ちします。

items.name: 【再世】next life-吴孟达

这是群星再世第四期，以后会不定期出去世的群星Lora，以纪念他们。

他是二当家，是黄金左脚，是训导主任，是重案组之虎曹达华，是咸蛋超人，是没有上车的达叔，是乌龙院大师兄……

香港著名影星，入行48年，在银幕上留下了无数经典形象，虽是配角，但演技极其出彩，每一个角色都刻画的活灵活现，演遍了市井小人物的悲欢离合，以不留痕迹的表演方式，稳坐香港配角第一交椅。

2021年罹患肝癌去世，享年68岁。

采用了180+图片训练这个lora，建议生成图片时，尺寸不要超过768*768，Lora权重建议0.8。

items.name: 2B (‎YoRHa No.2 Type B) game style
items.description:
Base model: Chilloutmix-Ni

Works with most Asian face checkpoint models, some Western face models also work, but the body ratio and the face are somewhat weird. The weight for my generate pics is 0.75

V2.0

  • Modified dataset, removing the yellowish and greyish looking

  • Modified reg set, changing background is much easier than the previous version

Reproduce the original game look of 2B in NieR: Automata, mainly focusing on her face, so no blindfold is offered in this version. The 0.65-0.9 range seems to work the best. The skirt and skirtless variants can be switched by using the "black skirt" and "white leotard" prompts. Highly recommend using it with Adetailer and Hires.fix, it helps face generation by a lot. Since there's only one outfit in my dataset, if you want to change the clothes, you need to use Lora block weight plugin to lower the corresponding weight.

着重还原游戏里2B的形象, 推荐权重0.6-0.8, 可以通过black skirt和white leotard的提示词来切换无裙子有有裙子版本. 最好能配合Adetailer和Hires.fix一起用, 能极大减少脸崩的可能性. 因为训练集就一套衣服, 所以衣服基本是过拟合的, 想换衣服得用Lora block weight去降低相应的权重

items.name: Brigitte Bardot (50s/60s)
items.description:
After 100 models, 404 hours of processing, 2200 likes and 16K downloads, I want to sincerely thank the 5 people in total who supported me and allowed me to credit my colab. You made all this possible and more is coming.

Brigitte Anne-Marie Bardot (born 28 September 1934), often referred to by her initials B.B., is a French animal rights activist and former actress, singer, and model. Famous for portraying sexually emancipated characters with hedonistic lifestyles, she was one of the best known sex symbols of the 1950s and 1960s. Although she withdrew from the entertainment industry in 1973, she remains a major popular culture icon.

This model is trained with SFW sources only. If you get NSFW content, you did it in purpose, didn't you?

Please provide constructive criticism.

You can support me here to be able to render better models (https://ko-fi.com/djo226). Supporters can request model.

Join my new Discord here! https://discord.gg/cnVvnkgtPb

Jordyn Jones (Face & Body LoRA) - influencer, dancer, former OnlyFans model. This LoRA includes Jordyn's face AND body. Use the trigger words to get the desired result. Infinite Jordyn pics await you. (All images & models are prompted with 18+ descriptions & trained with 18+ models!)

Read Me!

  • Jordyn Jones RHM v1: Trained on Real Hot Mix, my own mix. I use this LoRA for extremely high quality photorealistic results

    • For txt2img & img2img: LoRA weight between 0.9-1 for best results

  • Jordyn Jones SD1.5 v1: Trained on SD 1.5 base model, compatible with all models

    • For txt2img & img2img: LoRA weight between 0.5-1 depending on checkpoint model for best results (lower for anime/non-photorealistic models)

Recommended Settings

  • Hires fix: 0.2-0.3 for face, 0.2-0.4 for full body

  • Face is best at 1:1 resolution (make sure inpainting is 1:1 resolution)

    • Other resolutions work as well (see Training Info: resolution sizing for training dataset aspect ratio info)

  • 'makeup' is a trigger word. Put it in negative to get Jordyn with no makeup (somewhat accurate)

  • SOMETIMES:

    • Jordyn may generate with a bunch of freckles/birthmarks. If this happens, you can put 'freckles' in negative and/or edit out the freckles using inpainting/photo editor

    • Photos may appear slightly picture perfect/oversaturated for outdoor prompts. If this happens, you can put '(oversaturated:1.5), (colorful:1.5)' in negative

Training Info

  • 5 epochs, 25 repeats, 39 images

    • 26 face, 13 full body pics

  • For resolution sizing, enable buckets = true (25 = 1 image)

    • bucket 0: resolution (384, 640), count: 50

      bucket 1: resolution (384, 768), count: 25

      bucket 2: resolution (448, 576), count: 150

      bucket 3: resolution (448, 640), count: 25

      bucket 4: resolution (448, 704), count: 150

      bucket 5: resolution (512, 640), count: 225

      bucket 6: resolution (576, 576), count: 350

Background

I've been experimenting with LoRA training and seem to have found a sweet spot for epic photoreal accuracy for people. I made Belle last week, now here's Jordyn. Best Jordyn LoRA on Civit!

items.description:
Character Lora of Priscilla from The Witcher 3 : Wild Hunt

"Let's show 'em what real art is." -Priscilla

Daayyum.. this girl can sing -soul3142


This work is licensed under a Creative Commons Attribution-NonCommercial-NoDerivatives 4.0 International License.

If you want to, you can support me on Patreon or Buy me Coffee.

My Witcher LoRA Index - soul3142's Guide to the Witcher Universe.

Main Trigger Word - priscillaW3 , check examples for other ones.

Recommendations :-

  1. Highres Fix - must, if you are getting blurry and ugly images

    My upscale method: txt2img 512x768 -> send to img2img -> controlnet tile upscale, tile diffusion 2x scale with 4xUltrasharp upscaler and tiled vae

  2. Weight: 0.7 - 0.8

  3. Clip Skip: 2

  4. Steps: 25-30

  5. CFG: 7-8

  6. Denoising - Don't go too high, it can alter a lot of details

I use 0.7 weight, 25 steps, Euler a, Clip skip 2 in nearly all my examples with almost same, simple +ve/-ve prompts regardless of checkpoint for my own consistency purposes.

There are imperfections here & there, which i usually leave it in as is, (i never do any inpainting in examples), most of which like hands can be fixed with better prompting, negative embeddings while other like weapons are just bad majority of the time no matter the model as of today.

Some LoRA's are flexible with any clothing, some are not (usually character's with single costume) so keep these things in mind.

This is an unofficial fanmade LoRA, not intended for any commercial purpose and use. All characters and IP rights are owned by their respective creators and owners. I do not own rights to any of these characters.
